# Requires branch protection on main with "Require review from Code Owners"
# enabled (Settings -> Branches -> main -> a repo-admin action, not something
# a CI workflow or agent session can turn on) for these entries to actually
# block a merge. Until that's enabled, this file is documentation only.

# The integrity-audit safety net itself: any PR touching these must be
# reviewed by a human before merge, per audit/PLAYBOOK.md's never-list
# (never self-merge an audit PR).
/scripts/audit.py            @fandamentals
/scripts/audit_guard.py       @fandamentals
/scripts/audit_checks/        @fandamentals
/audit/                       @fandamentals
/.github/workflows/audit-guard.yml   @fandamentals
/.github/workflows/integrity.yml     @fandamentals

# Pipeline memory -- never hand-edited, per CLAUDE.md house rules.
/data/registers/               @fandamentals
/data/seen-items.json          @fandamentals
